o find alternate routes to your goals.<br></li><li>Choice and consequence – your decisions will have impact on the world around you.<br></li><li>Grenade crafting and Medicine making. Use ingredients to create various grenades and medicinal pills.<br></li><li>Watch morale of your teammates! Morale makes your allies more efficient in battle and out of battle.<br></li><li>3 difficulty modes – Casual, Hardy, and Dystopia.</li></ul><br>If you want to support this game and all my other past and future games further, please check out my patreon page below!<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.patreon.com/matthewashworth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >https://www.patreon.com/matthewashworth</a>",
